Date of Birth: December 11, 1896<br/>
Birthplace: Mesa, Arizona, USA<br/>
Ordained apostle:October 5, 1950<br/>
Death: August 19, 1978<br/>
<br/>
Born Dec. 11, 1896, at Mesa, Maricopa Co., Arizona, to Orley S. Stapley and Polly M. Hurisaker. Ordained apostle Oct. 5, 1950, by George Albert Smith, at age 53; died Aug. 19, 1978, at Salt Lake City, Salt Lake Co., Utah, at age 81.